comments: Lautite and \href{current_web_home_dir/ABC_oP12_62_c_c_c-003}{MnCuP} have the same AFLOW label, ABC\_oP12\_62\_c\_c\_c. The structures are generated by the same symmetry operations with different sets of parameters ({\tt --params}) specified in their corresponding CIF files.
